{"tid":1742844,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"西記者:C.朗拿度今年拿不到歐冠盃就將離開祖記 回歸曼聯","createTime":"2019-11-21T03:08:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T21:28:19.000Z","uid":173952,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"fec57a07e12406132c565897e2c5c0e7d414a068","tid":1742844,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:08:56.000Z","msg":"在「La Sexta」電視頻道的《Chiringuito De Jugones》節目中，西班牙媒體嘉賓Eduardo Inda聲稱，如果今季拿不到歐冠盃，那麼C.朗拿度將尋求離開祖雲達斯，返回曼聯踢球。<br />\n<br />\n  「C.朗拿度可能在賽季結束後離開祖雲達斯，如果他們不能拿到歐冠盃的話。」Eduardo Inda說，「他到拖連奴，就是為了嘗試在第三傢俱樂部拿到歐冠盃，但祖記的情況正在變得複雜起來。」<br />\n<br />\n  「祖記現在想簽普巴和麥巴比，我認為這會是非常困難的，尤其是第二筆交易。由於工資上的限制，如果祖記想簽新的大牌球員，他們不得不允許C.朗拿度離隊，因此這種可能性（C.朗拿度離隊）正在變大。」<br />\n<br />\n  C.朗拿度從2003年到2009年在曼聯效力六年，和紅魔有著感情橋樑，而曼聯有財力簽下葡萄牙人，一旦真有這種機會，雙方恐怕都會認真考慮。"},{"pid":"d07eb0e607ae8c4faa1a9ea31a54a55693accc16","tid":1742844,"uid":59283,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:12:41.000Z","msg":"返去爭霸氣盃？"},{"pid":"f2d9676dee69014d9fda443aedbc4467c951198f","tid":1742844,"uid":45772,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:13:05.000Z","msg":"愛回家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd02660e5f49e6486b821d8bb51d00f0fa95a28","tid":1742844,"uid":50744,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:13:39.000Z","msg":"朗哥返曼聯就好睇"},{"pid":"7a338b304b30b854620eed12f59ba89103de8f97","tid":1742844,"uid":120660,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:14:38.000Z","msg":"根本想返曼聯養老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809cba7628cd5e6e9a509da3c42e62144f087d4e","tid":1742844,"uid":52571,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:17:27.000Z","msg":"背叛佩雷斯既下場 <br />\n你認下錯咪考慮買返你囉"},{"pid":"26b3ab97304ba2a5e3afa8cf2aaa10ddbae3ac6e","tid":1742844,"uid":88461,"like":61,"dislike":0,"score":61,"quote":{"pid":"809cba7628cd5e6e9a509da3c42e62144f087d4e","tid":1742844,"uid":52571,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:17:27.000Z","msg":"背叛佩雷斯既下場 <br />\n你認下錯咪考慮買返你囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:18:36.000Z","msg":"6樓肉酸狗"},{"pid":"5f0f6083c4eaa9cf99529c4e4d857261f85dccbb","tid":1742844,"uid":48222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:19:09.000Z","msg":"返曼聯都唔會攞到歐聯架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返皇馬機會都仲大d"},{"pid":"88da92084dac99d704e4d7a21992411661850eaf","tid":1742844,"uid":127454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:19:35.000Z","msg":"咁就快有新版波衫賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65bfe5331367c11fe118233dba2f63b65481dea3","tid":1742844,"uid":50744,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"5f0f6083c4eaa9cf99529c4e4d857261f85dccbb","tid":1742844,"uid":48222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:19:09.000Z","msg":"返曼聯都唔會攞到歐聯架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返皇馬機會都仲大d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:20:59.000Z","msg":"返皇馬要交貨<br />\n返曼聯唔洗"},{"pid":"95766f8a5584f754ac5d0523b77b0a583bf2aff8","tid":1742844,"uid":43785,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:35:22.000Z","msg":"邊個會去曼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又撞番bale<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4274b773bb759ee6a8c5c6e5b2b38def0fbf497a","tid":1742844,"uid":12086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:36:24.000Z","msg":"咪仲難左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f0cc7efc2ceff2ca7f82e97a620e935288edb81","tid":1742844,"uid":39218,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:37:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>在「La Sexta」電視頻道的《Chiringuito De Jugones》節目中，西班牙媒體嘉賓Eduardo Inda聲稱，如果今季拿不到歐冠盃，那麼C.朗拿度將尋求離開祖雲達斯，返回曼聯踢球。<br />\n<br />\n  「C.朗拿度可能在賽季結束後離開祖雲達斯，如果他們不能拿到歐冠盃的話。」Eduardo Inda說，「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他到拖連奴</span></span>，就是為了嘗試在第三傢俱樂部拿到歐冠盃，但祖記的情況正在變得複雜起來。」<br />\n<br />\n  「祖記現在想簽普巴和麥巴比，我認為這會是非常困難的，尤其是第二筆交易。由於工資上的限制，如果祖記想簽新的大牌球員，他們不得不允許C.朗拿度離隊，因此這種可能性（C.朗拿度離隊）正在變大。」<br />\n<br />\n  C.朗拿度從2003年到2009年在曼聯效力六年，和紅魔有著感情橋樑，而曼聯有財力簽下葡萄牙人，一旦真有這種機會，雙方恐怕都會認真考慮。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48d1713dce63f81b7ff8c19f28a5b7536f5379d","tid":1742844,"uid":4349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:38:04.000Z","msg":"番黎曼係想高薪養老, 得閒屌下英國妹<br />\n唔想再煩爭冠咁解"},{"pid":"d48b4301de1fe1064256a30a57fdad87f647e272","tid":1742844,"uid":271659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:39:10.000Z","msg":"繼續吹"},{"pid":"7b62d5fb98ad7d21b504a565d04fbc5bbd80c7d7","tid":1742844,"uid":7075,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"9f0cc7efc2ceff2ca7f82e97a620e935288edb81","tid":1742844,"uid":39218,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:37:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>在「La Sexta」電視頻道的《Chiringuito De Jugones》節目中，西班牙媒體嘉賓Eduardo Inda聲稱，如果今季拿不到歐冠盃，那麼C.朗拿度將尋求離開祖雲達斯，返回曼聯踢球。<br />\n<br />\n  「C.朗拿度可能在賽季結束後離開祖雲達斯，如果他們不能拿到歐冠盃的話。」Eduardo Inda說，「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他到拖連奴</span></span>，就是為了嘗試在第三傢俱樂部拿到歐冠盃，但祖記的情況正在變得複雜起來。」<br />\n<br />\n  「祖記現在想簽普巴和麥巴比，我認為這會是非常困難的，尤其是第二筆交易。由於工資上的限制，如果祖記想簽新的大牌球員，他們不得不允許C.朗拿度離隊，因此這種可能性（C.朗拿度離隊）正在變大。」<br />\n<br />\n  C.朗拿度從2003年到2009年在曼聯效力六年，和紅魔有著感情橋樑，而曼聯有財力簽下葡萄牙人，一旦真有這種機會，雙方恐怕都會認真考慮。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:41:20.000Z","msg":"知唔知祖係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":