0662c247546ab07f6d479479dc8fc06daf2db32","tid":1742844,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f0f6083c4eaa9cf99529c4e4d857261f85dccbb","tid":1742844,"uid":48222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:19:09.000Z","msg":"返曼聯都唔會攞到歐聯架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返皇馬機會都仲大d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:03:50.000Z","msg":"應該係放棄返去養老㗎喇"},{"pid":"e455e2db3612930e4b89b14e2aacdadf6097454d","tid":1742844,"uid":245064,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f0cc7efc2ceff2ca7f82e97a620e935288edb81","tid":1742844,"uid":39218,"like":1,"dislike":20,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:37:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>在「La Sexta」電視頻道的《Chiringuito De Jugones》節目中，西班牙媒體嘉賓Eduardo Inda聲稱，如果今季拿不到歐冠盃，那麼C.朗拿度將尋求離開祖雲達斯，返回曼聯踢球。<br />\n<br />\n  「C.朗拿度可能在賽季結束後離開祖雲達斯，如果他們不能拿到歐冠盃的話。」Eduardo Inda說，「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他到拖連奴</span></span>，就是為了嘗試在第三傢俱樂部拿到歐冠盃，但祖記的情況正在變得複雜起來。」<br />\n<br />\n  「祖記現在想簽普巴和麥巴比，我認為這會是非常困難的，尤其是第二筆交易。由於工資上的限制，如果祖記想簽新的大牌球員，他們不得不允許C.朗拿度離隊，因此這種可能性（C.朗拿度離隊）正在變大。」<br />\n<br />\n  C.朗拿度從2003年到2009年在曼聯效力六年，和紅魔有著感情橋樑，而曼聯有財力簽下葡萄牙人，一旦真有這種機會，雙方恐怕都會認真考慮。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:03:55.000Z","msg":"其實都靈同拖連奴應該係兩樣嘢嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f4f0035f4d4d27c197b964779bd0cd17897c208","tid":1742844,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60662c247546ab07f6d479479dc8fc06daf2db32","tid":1742844,"uid":13724,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f0f6083c4eaa9cf99529c4e4d857261f85dccbb","tid":1742844,"uid":48222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:19:09.000Z","msg":"返曼聯都唔會攞到歐聯架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返皇馬機會都仲大d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T08:03:50.000Z"